data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
Author: Dennis Lang 2009 https://landenlabs.com
Credits: This application is based off of Leonardo Paneque "Solution Cleaner" http://www.teknowmagic.net/
Description: Locate files which match selected file and directory filters and allow the 'located' file list to be pruned before deletion. Use right-click on all Lists to Popup auxilary menu actions. You can export ALL lists as a Comma-Separated-Value (CSV) file.
Keyboard: Control-A to select all rows in List Space to toggle check boxes Delete to delete selected items Up/Down to navigate up/down list and select row.
Warning: If compiled as "Any CPU" there is no undo to restore deleted items.
